		(property "Description" "SparkFun I<sup>2</sup>C Standard Pinout Header SparkFun has standardized on a pinout for all I<sup>2</sup>C based sensor breakouts.<br><br>This pinout allows I<sup>2</sup>C boards to be plugged directly into the headers on Arduino Uno compatible boards, andto be daisy chained easily. <b>Example SparkFun Products:</b><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.sparkfun.com/products/13676\">SparkFun Atmospheric Sensor Breakout - BME280</a></li><li><a href= https://www.sparkfun.com/products/11084 >SparkFun Altitude/Pressure Sensor Breakout - MPL3115A2</a></li><li><a href= https://www.sparkfun.com/products/12785 >SparkFun TOF Range Finder Sensor - VL6180</a></li></ul>"
